title: Bags, Books & Bling and Everything in Between
desc:
Calling ALL NYC, NJ, PA, CT, DE, MD Ladies and Small Business Women. An afternoon to support and shop with other small business women including authors,owners and direct sales consultants/ representatives. We will also exchange business cards, ideas and tips on being successful in business. You will also have the opportunity to do some last minute holiday shopping. Games. Door Prizes. Surprises. Raffles & Giveaways will be apart of a wonderful Sunday Afternoon. Bring your positive energy and a friend and get a FREE gift.? 
 Lite Refreshments will be served. 
 Admission: $5.00 rebate 
 You will get $5.00 off your first purchase so it's like attending for FREE.
